channel.title: Coder needed!
channel.description: Hi guys, I am looking for a coder this person must have experience and i have team viewer as well. The person will be rewarded with co-owner and admin on forums. Also if you are experienced with GFX and could make a backround for my server please PM for some rewards. Thank you i will be really grateful. P.S If you want to stay in my server as co-owner you will receive half of the donations. + it would be really awesome if it were a .jar or downloadable content and i have portfoward and all. Thanks.
